title: Database Tour Pro 8.2.8.23 + Patch - Crackingpatching
description:
Description: 
Database Tour Pro 8.2.8.23 Allows you to work with different databases, and also get a large number of utilities useful when editing the database. For example, the SQL tool, the report creation tool, database conversion, export, import and so on. 
As a result, we get a good software for working with Interbase, Firebird, Microsoft Access, Microsoft Excel, Oracle, SQL Server and other databases, viewing and editing is as convenient and understandable as possible, you can automate frequent operations, you can work through the command line, print, export data. 
It is a pity that Vitaly Levchenko forgot to add Russian support, the interface is multilanguage, there is the Ukrainian language, but there is no Russian. 

Developer: Vitaliy Levchenko Software 
License: ShareWare - for you free of charge 
Language: English - Russian version and Russifier not available 
File size: 5.48 MB 
OS: Windows 

How to Install: 
1). Instructions are included in ReadMe.txt if needed. 
2). Thats all, Done & enjoy
